FYI - 

Met Land Development Company, LLC, a Delaware limited liability company (owned 100% by Enron North America Corp) was a shelf company we initially formed for a potential project in New York.  This entity is now being used in connection with owning the Siemens Westinghouse 501D5A.

Kathleen
